01:02:04,800 --> 01:02:10,000
I'm going to pick Die by Kieran Gillen, Stephanie Hans and Clayton Cowles.

877
01:02:10,000 --> 01:02:13,940
Die is a comic that was published between 2018 and 2021.

878
01:02:13,940 --> 01:02:19,400
It was a three-time finalist for the Hugo Award for Best Graphic Story or Comic.

879
01:02:19,400 --> 01:02:21,680
And it won the British Fantasy Award.

880
01:02:21,680 --> 01:02:23,100
And I had not read it.

881
01:02:23,100 --> 01:02:26,040
